summary: An Ordinance, authorizing John S. Bragnall and others, to improve that portion of the alley adjoining Lot One (1), and the north ten (10) feet of the west fifty (50) feet of Lot Two (2), in Block twenty-nine (29), Law's Second Addition to Seattle, by grading and paving the same with suitable material at their own expense and in accordance with plans to be approved by the Board of Public Works under certain terms and conditions.
